BIKE TRIP AND CHERRY BLOSSOM VIEWING TRIP

415
00:23:36,182 --> 00:23:36,792
WHEN ENJOYING CAMPING,
BE SURE TO FOLLOW THE RULES

416
00:23:36,793 --> 00:23:37,401
OF THE CAMPGROUND AND ITS FACILITIES.

417
00:23:37,402 --> 00:23:38,504
